            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%8D%AF%E5%B8%88%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E5%A5%A5%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%96%E9%9F%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%84%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%94%A8%E8%8D%AF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%8D%AF%E5%B8%88%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E5%A5%A5%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%96%E9%9F%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%84%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%94%A8%E8%8D%AF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#药师提醒奥司他韦不可作为常规预防用药#</span></a>】近期流感高发，不少小伙伴会自行服用"奥司他韦"预防流感。药师介绍，①与甲流、乙流患者密切接触后48小时内，可服用"奥司他韦"进行预防；②部分患者服药后会有胃肠道反应或神经毒性，不建议作为常规预防用药；③服用“奥司他韦”可能会影响接种流感疫苗，要留心时间间隔。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（江苏新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4977813477064764" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">江苏新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/001q6ELGly8hkpz3d5w4sj61hc0u0n5u02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/68YBsjxRlx08aRwlhsNq01041200qPqv0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1702473265&amp;ssig=G%2BH2CR2UZT&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/f1ZnleTelx08aRwjv9cA01041200dQWB0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1702473265&amp;ssig=SkP1LU7xx3&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.w